@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<style>
    body {
        background-color: #f4f7e7;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        color: #3e4e1f;
    }

    h1, h2 {
        color: #556b2f;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(85, 107, 47, 0.3);
    }

    p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #3e4e1f;
    }

    .highlight {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #667a2a;
    }
</style>

<div class="about-container">
    <h1>About AgriEnergy Connect</h1>

    <p>
        <span class="highlight">AgriEnergy Connect</span> is an innovative web-based platform designed to bridge the gap between
        South Africa's agriculture and renewable energy sectors. Our mission is to foster collaboration, sustainability,
        and innovation by providing a digital space where farmers and green technology companies can connect,
        share solutions, and drive progress.
    </p>

    <p>
        Built using the robust <span class="highlight">MVC (Model-View-Controller)</span> framework, AgriEnergy Connect enables users to easily
        interact with a clean, secure, and scalable platform. We empower farmers to register, post their products,
        and engage with energy providers interested in sustainable practices and agricultural synergy.
    </p>

    <p>
        Through this project, we aim to support South Africa’s environmental goals by promoting
        <span class="highlight">clean energy integration</span> in farming operations, improving productivity while reducing carbon footprints.
        Together, we envision a future where agriculture and green energy are seamlessly intertwined for the benefit of both people and the planet.
    </p>
</div>
